# Defense-in-depth: PEM keys must not be committed to the chaos-lab repo path.
# Phase 120-02 (PUBREPO-LAB-KEYS) — `ca.key` and `client.key` are now generated
# on first `./lab.sh up` by `ensure_lab_certs` in lab.sh; do not check them in.
#
# Note: scenario fixtures (modern/legacy/expired/selfsigned/keycloak/mtls/
# scenarios/* .key files) are pre-tracked intentional chaos fixtures and are
# NOT covered by this exclusion at HEAD — git ignore only applies to untracked
# paths. New .key/.crt/.srl files in this directory will be ignored by default.
*.key
*.crt
*.srl
